CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 20, 1962, pg. 10 reads:" 'Y' Ranch hands In Big '62 Round-Up - Yellow Circle - Ranch riders of the Yellow Circle Ranch are shown receiving their assignments from Robert L. Edwards Jr., ranch rider. Left to right: Laurence Washington, Ollie David, Laurence Cosby, W.H. Coleman, ranch leader; W.A. Arvin, Albert Zigler, Alfred Stewart and Edwards."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Laurence Washington, Ollie David, Laurence Cosby, W.H. Coleman, W.A. Arvin, Albert Zigler, Alfred Stewart and Robert L. Edwards Jr., standing in Centre Avenue YMCA during 1962 membership campaign
